comment:
* Represents the usage statistics of a device {@link android.content.res.Configuration} for a
 * specific time range.

methods.name: public long getFirstTimeStamp()
methods.comment:
* Get the beginning of the time range this {@link ConfigurationStats} represents,
     * measured in milliseconds since the epoch.
     * <p/>
     * See {@link System#currentTimeMillis()}.

methods.name: public long getLastTimeStamp()
methods.comment:
* Get the end of the time range this {@link ConfigurationStats} represents,
     * measured in milliseconds since the epoch.
     * <p/>
     * See {@link System#currentTimeMillis()}.

methods.name: public long getLastTimeActive()
methods.comment:
* Get the last time this configuration was active, measured in milliseconds since the epoch.
     * <p/>
     * See {@link System#currentTimeMillis()}.

methods.name: public long getTotalTimeActive()
methods.comment: * Get the total time this configuration was active, measured in milliseconds.

methods.name: public int getActivationCount()
methods.comment: * Get the number of times this configuration was active.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
